watch.expression: # get word location in vocabulary@LINE@def words2vocab_indices(words, vocab_dict, UNK_IDENTIFIER):@LINE@ if isinstance(words, str):@LINE@ vocab_indices = [vocab_dict[words] if words in vocab_dict else vocab_dict[UNK_IDENTIFIER]]@LINE@ else:@LINE@ vocab_indices = [(vocab_dict[w] if w in vocab_dict else vocab_dict[UNK_IDENTIFIER])@LINE@ for w in words]@LINE@ return vocab_indices
